<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      metal:use-macro="api.macro('kotti:templates/view/master.pt')">

  <article metal:fill-slot="content" class="splash-page-view content">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span7">
            <img src="http://placekitten.com/500/300" />
        </div>
        <div class="span5">
        <h1>${context.title} Splash Page</h1>
        <p class="description">
        <p>
          Congratulations, you have succesfully installed <a href="http://github.com/koansys/kotti_splashpage"><code>kotti_splashpage</code></a>.
          Now you probably want to set a renderer. You can do so by adding something like the following to your application deployment configuration (ini file):
        </p>
        <p>
          <pre>
kotti_splashpage.renderer =
    mypackage:templates/splash-page.pt
          </pre>
        </p>
        </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">

    </div>
  </article>

</html>
